2%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20recruiter%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20company%20primarily%20uses%20an%20internal%20database%20to%20find%20candidates%2C%20but%20the%20second-most%20popular%20way%20to%20scout%20potential%20employees%20is%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20build%20out%20your%20profile%20and%20use%20it%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20who%20already%20work%20there%20and%20can%20give%20you%20a%20referral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recruiter%20said%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20stand%20out%20among%20Google's%20candidate%20pool%20is%20to%20network%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20approach.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20job%20candidates%20should%20email%20hiring%20managers%20directly%20to%20make%20a%20connection%20and%20then%20steer%20the%20conversation%20to%20express%20interest%20in%20a%20specific%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recruiter%20also%20encouraged%20job%20applicants%20to%20tailor%20their%20resumes%20to%20individual%20job%20descriptions%20and%2C%20during%20the%20interview%20process%2C%20describe%20details%20of%20how%20they%20solved%20a%20problem%20in%20a%20past%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220079ac7c-8327-4980-bf2f-4a68ec4e0dd6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20hired%20at%20Google%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20known%20throughout%20the%20tech%20industry%20for%20having%20a%20lengthy%2C%20difficult%20hiring%20process%2C%20and%20for%20being%20ultra-selective%20about%20its%20candidates.%20Of%20the%202%20million%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-google-looks-for-in-employees-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20applications%20Google%20receives%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20year%2C%20it%20hires%20roughly%204%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20bases%20its%20hiring%20decisions%20on%20four%20key%20metrics%3A%20job-related%20skills%2C%20general%20cognitive%20ability%2C%20leadership%20abilities%20(even%20for%20non-managerial%20roles!)%2C%20and%20what%20the%20company%20calls%20%26quot%3BGoogleyness%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20how%20well%20your%20personality%20will%20fit%20in%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Google%20executives%20and%20recruiters%20have%20defined%20%26quot%3BGoogleyness%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20mixture%20of%20proactiveness%2C%20positivity%2C%20humility%2C%20playfulness%2C%20conscientiousness%2C%20and%20openness%20to%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20employees%20walk%20across%20the%20campus%20of%20the%20Googleplex%2C%20Google's%20headquarters%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662fd08c10dfcda4096488fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoogle%20prizes%20a%20quality%20among%20workers%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BGoogleyness%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20personality%20traits%20like%20being%20open%20to%20learning%20and%20being%20humble.%3Cp%3EMelina%20Mara%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20also%20has%20a%20multi-step%20hiring%20process.%20It%20encourages%20people%20to%20start%20by%20self-reflecting%20on%20what%20they%20truly%20want%20out%20of%20a%20career.%20Then%2C%20search%20and%20apply%20for%20a%20job%20on%20the%20company's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20suggests%20applicants%20build%20a%20job-specific%20resume%20that%20ties%20their%20skills%20and%20experience%20to%20the%20job%20requirements.%20Including%20data%20to%20illustrate%20your%20successes%20in%20managing%20projects%20will%20help%20your%20resume%20stand%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Google%20engineer%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-tips-google-software-engineer-skills-experience-careers-software-tech-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20the%20resume%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20helped%20him%20land%20a%20%24300%2C000%20job%20at%20the%20company%20recom