f-to-give-training-on-whistleblower-laws-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCan%20Rohit%20Do%20It%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Harbhajan's%20Dhoni%20Reminder%2C%20Urges%20Team%20To%20Play%20As%20'We'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20nearing%20its%20conclusion%2C%20Indian%20cricketers%20are%20set%20to%20shift%20gears%20and%20start%20preparations%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20With%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20leading%20the%20side%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20would%20hope%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20in%20the%20marquee%20event%2C%20unlike%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20where%20a%20defeat%20in%20the%20final%20against%20Australia%20ended%20the%20big%20dream.%20While%20Team%20India%20has%20the%20star%20power%20in%20all%20departments%20of%20the%20game%2C%20former%20India%20cricketer%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20has%20urged%20the%20team%20to%20play%20as%20unit%2C%20putting%20'we'%20in%20front%20of%20'I'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20on%20Star%20Sports%2C%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20recalled%20how%20senior%20players%20rallied%20around%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20ICC%20World%20T20%20in%202007%2C%20giving%20him%20ample%20support%20and%20guidance%20to%20succeed%20as%20a%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20many%20people%20know%2C%20Dhoni%20was%20a%20very%20new%20captain%2C%20so%20he%20needed%20that%20support%20from%20all%20of%20us.%20Before%20matches%20against%20teams%20like%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20England%2C%20our%20core%20group%20would%20get%20together%20during%20the%20game%20to%20strategize%20for%20the%20next%20few%20overs.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20a%20match%20against%20Australia%2C%20I%20bowled%20the%20crucial%2017th%20or%2018th%20overs%20because%20if%20we%20managed%20to%20give%20away%20only%204%20runs%2C%20it%20saved%20us%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harbhajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20batters%20didn't%20score%2025%20runs%20in%20an%20over%20unlike%20today.%20The%20decision-making%20was%20always%20a%20team%20effort.%20When%20you%20play%20together%20as%20a%20united%20team%2C%20you%20win%20more%20competitions.%20Dhoni%20was%20a%20great%20listener%2C%20taking%20collective%20decisions%20that%20benefited%20the%20team.%20It%20was%20never%20about%20individual%20performances%20but%20about%20playing%20as%20'we'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%20asked%20if%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20under%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20could%20do%20something%20similar%20and%20achieve%20collective%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20the%20question%20now%20is%2C%20can%20Rohit%20Sharma%20do%20it%3F%20Rohit%20is%20not%20alone%3B%20it's%20about%20'we'.%20If%20we%20play%20as%20a%20united%20team%2C%20thinking%20about%20collective%20success%20rather%20than%20individual%20achievements%2C%20then%20we%20can%20win.%20But%20if%20we%20only%20focus%20on%20personal%20goals%2C%20things%20become%20difficult.%20It's%20all%20about%20the%20'we'%20mentality%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20things%20come%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhajji.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715948220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7kdiapfg_rohit-sharma_625x300_17_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fcan-rohit-sharma-do-it-harbhajan-singh-drops-ms-dhoni-reminder-urges-india-to-play-as-we-5681935%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Harbhajan%20Singh%20recalled%20MS%20Dhoni's%20success%20as%20captain%20during%20the%20early%20days%2C%20highlighting%20how%20he%20always%20put%20the%20team%20in%20front.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%2