lping%20women%20build%20wealth.%20According%20to%20her%20website%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%202%20million%20women%20save%2C%20and%20that%20number%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20featured%20in%20the%20Netflix%20documentary%20%26quot%3BGet%20Smart%20With%20Money%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20led%20seminars%20on%20financial%20wellness%20for%20women%2C%20and%20has%20pushed%20to%20get%20financial%20education%20into%20our%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Amanda%20Wolfe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshewolfeofwallstreet.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmanda%20Wolfe's%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspiring%20story%20of%20growing%20up%20poor%20with%20parents%20who%20used%20drugs%20is%20the%20hook%20that%20pulls%20you%20in%2C%20but%20what%20will%20make%20you%20stay%20is%20the%20way%20she%20shares%20and%20presents%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrimarily%20an%20Instagram%20creator%2C%20she%20has%20made%20traditionally%20difficult-to-understand%20financial%20information%20accessible%20and%20convenient.%20Her%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Should%20I%20Do%20with%20My%20Salary%26quot%3B%20series%20breaks%20down%20how%20real%20people%20spend%20their%20money%20and%20recommends%20what%20they%20should%20do%20differently.%20Her%20investing%20workshop%20(or%20party%2C%20as%20she%20calls%20it)%20is%20free%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Cindy%20Zuniga-Sanchez%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzero-basedbudget.com%2F%5C%22%3ECindy%20Zuniga-Sanchez%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20her%20blog%2C%20the%20Zero-Based%20Budget%2C%20to%20document%20her%20debt%20freedom%20journey.%20After%20law%20school%2C%20she%20was%20nearly%20%24215%2C000%20in%20debt%20and%20used%20a%20zero-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbudgeting%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20approach%20to%20pay%20it%20all%20off%20in%2048%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20content%20about%20debt%20%E2%80%9