0bottom%20of%20my%20heart.%20My%20head%20is%20bowed%20in%20reverence%20before%20you.%20You%20have%20given%20me%20the%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20as%20an%20MP%20for%2020%20years.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20asset%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%2053%2C%20will%20square%20off%20against%20BJP's%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRaebareli%20is%20my%20family%2C%20similarly%20Amethi%20is%20also%20my%20home.%20Not%20only%20are%20the%20tender%20memories%20of%20my%20life%20associated%20with%20this%20place%20but%20the%20roots%20of%20our%20family%20are%20also%20connected%20to%20this%20soil%20for%20the%20last%20100%20years.%20This%20relationship%2C%20as%20sacred%20as%20Mother%20Ganga%2C%20started%20with%20the%20farmers'%20movement%20of%20Awadh%20and%20Raebareli%20which%20continues%20till%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20Hindi%2C%20with%20daughter%20Priyanka%20and%20son%20Rahul%20standing%20right%20behind%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prestige%20seat%20has%20been%20represented%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20grandmother%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20grandfather%2C%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20nearby%20Amethi%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Amethi%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20is%20pitted%20against%20Congress%20candidate%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20longtime%20loyalist%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20came%20here%20for%20the%20first%20time%2042%20years%20ago%20with%20my%20father%20(Rajiv%20Gandhi).%20Whatever%20I%20have%20learned%20about%20politics%2C%20it%20has%20been%20taught%20to%20me%20by%20the%20Amethi%20public.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20were%20no%20roads%20and%20no%20development.%20And%20I%20have%20witnessed%20the%20relationship%20of%20love%20between%20the%20people%20here%20