nd%20one%20would%20get%20mine%3B%20we'd%20flip%20a%20coin%20for%20who%20went%20first.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20pregnant%20with%20our%20first%20child%2C%20I%20remembered%20all%20the%20teasing%20I'd%20gotten%20as%20a%20kid.%20How%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpicked-son-baby-name-unique-no-longer-trendy-angry-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20couldn't%20spell%20my%20last%20name%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20give%20all%20the%20kids%20your%20surname%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said%20to%20my%20spouse.%20Middle%20names%20would%20be%20from%20the%20maternal%20side%20of%20the%20family%2C%20we%20decided.%20This%20organizing%20principle%20worked%20well.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20we%20planned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadoption-is-my-first-choice-for-motherhood-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadopt%20a%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20our%20fourth%2C%20only%20one%20through%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df00dccc-4aea-4a3b-bbab-b44dd16059e3%5C%22%3EWe%20chose%20the%20name%20with%20the%20birth%20mother%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20a%20month%20before%20this%20baby%20was%20due%2C%20our%20shared%20social%20worker%20gathered%20us%20and%20Caroline%2C%20the%20intended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmet-birth-mother-heal-abandonment-issues-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20pregnant.%20We%20all%20planned%20on%20an%20open%20adoption.%20Our%20social%20worker%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20thinking%20about%20the%20name%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-pregnancy-side-effects-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20been%20pregnant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20would%20have%20placed%20my%20hand%20on%20my%20rounded%20belly%20just%20then.%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20this%20until%20I%20noticed%20my%20eyes%20went%20straight%20to%20Caroline's%20round%20belly.%20It%20was%20barely%20winter%2C%20but%20there%20was%20snow%20outside%2C%20and%20a%20bright%20sun%20streamed%20through%20the%20window%20across%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20like%20the%20name%20Jasmine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJasmine%20is%20really%20pretty%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20agreed%20immediately.%20I'd%20tossed%20that%20name%20out%20for%20a%20theoretical%20girl%20during%20other%20pregnancies.%20It%20hadn't%20stuck.%20By%20the%20time%20we%20sat%20around%20this%20dining%20table%2C%20I%20understood%20that%20I'd%20been%20waiting%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20for%20Saskia%20or%20Kezia%2C%20the%20original%20girl%20names%20we'd%20had%2C%20names%20my%20husband%2C%20Hosea%2C%20and%20I%20both%20still%20loved.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20two%20names%20we've%20thought%20about%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20If%20there's%20one%20you%20like%20more%20or%20that%20you%20hate%2C%20we%20want%20to%20know%3B%20we%20want%20you%20to%20love%20her%20name%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20Hosea%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%20Saskia%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20Kezia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaroline%20thought%20both%20names%20were%20pretty%2C%20and%20Hosea%20described%20how%20the%20kids%20had%20his%20surname%20and%20maternal%20side%20middle%20names%2C%20so%20we%20hoped%20she'd%20suggest%20a%20name%20from%20her%20family.%20Caroline%20shared%20her%20mother's%20maiden%20name%20with%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0149803-6d64-424a-96b6-dc54c17f21f9%5C%22%3EHer%20birth%20mother's%20maternal%20family%20name%20is%20her%20middle%20name%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20grew%20quieter%2C%20all%20of%20us.%20While%20the%20sun%20streamed%20in%2C%20it%20was%20quiet%20enough%20to%20take%20notice%20of%20the%20warmth%20beaming%20through%20the%20window%2C%20as%20if%20to%20support%20the%20hope%20that%20this%20shared%20name%20would%20carry%20this%20baby%20through%20the%20complexity%20of%20life%20begun%20with%20one%20parent%20and%20continued%20with%20others%2C%20knowing%20we%20all%20loved%20her%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20are%20really%20pretty%2C%26quot%3B%20Caroline%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20like%20Saskia%20a%20lot.%20Saskia%20Raine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20beautiful%2C%26quot%3B%20our%20social%20worker%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20weeks%20later%2C%20that%20full%20name%20was%20on%20the%20baby's%20birth%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20adoption%2C%20the%20birth%20certificate%20issued%20just%20after%20birth%20isn't%20the%20final%20one%2C%20though.%20Many%20months%20later%2C%20on%20a%20different%20early%20wintry%20day%20when%20huge%2C%20pounding%20rain%20fell%20atop%20slushy%20snow%2C%20her%20same%20full%20name%20appeared%20on%20her%20second%20birth%20certificate.%20This%20new%2C%20amended%20one%20issued%20after%20the%20adoption%20was%20finalized%20no%20longer%20listed%20Caroline.%20Instead%2C%20my%20husband's%20and%20my%20names%20appeared.%20I%20felt%20like%20all%20our%20names%20belonged.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20courthouse%2C%20adoption%20ceremonies%20are%20just%20about%20the%20only%20happy%20events%2C%20and%20the%20staff%20makes%20a%20big%20fuss.%20We%20were%20handed%20a%20Polaroid%20of%20our%20family%20with%20the%20judge%20in%20a%20clear%20plastic%20frame%2C%20along%20with%20a%20certificate.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20didn't%20tell%20a%20whole%20story.%20Neither%20birth%20certificate%20did.%20The%20name%20doesn't%20either%2C%20but%20it%20tries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnamed-baby-with-birth-mother-adoption-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715947082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664381929686a6f37bffaa3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnamed-baby-with-birth-mother-adoption-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20we%20adopted%20our%20fourth%20child%2C%20we%20chose%20her%20name%20with%20her%20birth%20mother.%20We%20wanted%20all%20our%20children%20to%20have%20a%20middle%20name%20from%20their%20maternal%20side.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Buttenwieser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnamed-baby-with-birth-mother-adoption-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pioneer%20Of%20Digital%20Democracy'%3A%20India%201st%20Country%20In%20The%20World%20To%20Use%20EVMs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%20but%20not%20many%20know%20that%20it%20is%20India%20that%20perfected%20and%20deployed%20mass%20electronic%20voting%20for%20the%20first%20time%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20So%2C%20the%20country%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20was%20also%20the%20pioneer%20of%20digital%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20on%20May%2019%2C%201982%2C%20that%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20were%20used%20in%20Kerala%20as%20a%20pilot%20project%20in%20the%20North%20Paravur%20constituency%2C%20where%2050%20out%20of%20the%2084%20polling%20stations%20used%20the%20first-ever%20secure%20direct%20digital%20vote%20recording%20device%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20second%20country%20to%20try%20EVMs%20was%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20almost%20a%20decade%20later%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Atlantic%20Council%2C%20a%20US-based%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEVMs%20and%20India%20have%20a%20fascinating%20history%3B%20they%20came%20well%20before%20the%20Information%20Technology%20revolution.%20IBM%20had%20just%20introduced%20personal%20computers%20in%20the%20USA%20a%20few%20months%20earlier%20when%20India%20got%20EVMs%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Professor%20Rajeeva%20L%20Karandikar%20from%20the%20Chennai%20Mathematical%20Institute%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20truthful%20machines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20us%20know%20that%20India%20invented%20the%20zero%20long%20eons%20ago%2C%20but%20more%20recently%2C%20in%201982%2C%20India%20became%20the%20world's%20first%20country%20to%20use%20that%20'zero'%20in%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20since%20electronics%20is%20all%20about%20zeroes%20and%20ones.%20Today%2C%20nearly%20a%20billion%20people%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%20on%20tamper-proof%20third-generation%20EVMs.%20So%20there%20should%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20India%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20democracy%20and%20today%20a%20digitally%20empowered%20democracy.%20India%20was%20a%20pioneer%20in%20using%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20and%20remains%20the%20fountainhead%20of%20innovation%20for%20secure%20electoral%20voting%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20a%20director%20of%20an%20IIT%20who%20is%20deeply%20involved%20in%20designing%20and%20securing%20the%20EVM%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEVMs%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20India%20as%20they%20cannot%20lie%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20doubts%20about%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20asserted%20TS%20Krishnamurthy%2C%20a%20former%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20under%20whose%20tenure%20EVMs%20became%20universal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20just%20about%20twenty-five%20countries%20use%20digital%20voting.%20According%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20the%20countries%20using%20EVMs%20include%20the%20USA%2C%20Australia%2C%20Belgium%2C%20Bulgaria%2C%20Italy%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Canada%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Chile%2C%20Peru%2C%20Venezuela%2C%20Namibia%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Armenia%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%2C%20there%20are%20several%20types%20of%20digital%20voting.%20There%20is%20fully%20electronic%20voting%20like%20India%20has%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20systems%20where%20only%20the%20counting%20is%20electronic.%20Some%20countries%2C%20like%20Estonia%2C%20have%20started%20using%20internet-based%20remote%20voting%2C%20while%20others%20have%20internet-based%20voting%20at%20designated%20polling%20stations.%20Some%20use%20optical%20scanners%20with%20both%20networked%20and%20non-networked%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20countries%2C%20electronic%20voting%20devices%20are%20made%20by%20private%20companies%2C%20which%20are%20considered%20less%20cyber%20secure%20compared%20to%20the%20government-owned%20facilities%20in%20India%20that%20manufacture%20the%20EVMs.%20The%20world's%20most%20advanced%20country%2C%20the%20USA%2C%20uses%20several%20different%20forms%20of%20electronic%20voting%20and%20has%20no%20nationwide%20standard.%20Some%20believe%20that%20blockchain-based%20voting%20could%20be%20the%20way%20forward.%20Who%20knows%2C%20India%20could%20well%20enable%20Aadhaar-based%20voting%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20all%20internet-based%20voting%20is%20prone%20to%20cyber%20fraud%2C%20say%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20half%20the%20world's%20population%20is%20going%20to%20hold%20elections%2C%20but%20it%20is%20only%20in%20India%20that%20969%20million%20voters%20are%20eligible%20to%20cast%20their%20votes%2C%20and%20all%20of%20them%20will%20be%20recorded%20digitally%20in%20over%201.05%20million%20polling%20booths.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20first%20four%20phases%20of%20voting%2C%20ECI%20data%20shows%20that%20already%20451%20million%20Indians%20have%20cast%20their%20vote.%20To%20put%20this%20in%20perspective%2C%20the%20number%20of%20voters%20who%20have%20cast%20their%20vote%20digitally%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20is%20more%20than%20the%20entire%20population%20of%20the%20USA%2C%20which%20is%20about%20335%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202004%2C%20all%20Parliamentary%20elections%20have%20been%20conducted%20using%20EVMs%2C%20and%20ECI%20data%20indicates%20that%20some%203%2C200%20million%2C%20or%20320%20crore%2C%20votes%20in%20all%20have%20been%20cast%20to%20date%20on%20EVMs%E2%80%94a%20whopping%20number%E2%80%94and%20not%20even%20one%20recorded%20case%20of%20tampering%20has%20been%20proved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20several%20countries%20have%20initiated%20electronic%20voting%2C%20but%20some%20have%20given%20up%20after%20a%20short%20trial%20as%20they%20did%20not%20find%20them%20to%20be%20cyber%20secure.%20This%20includes%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20Germany%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20abandoned%20electronic%20voting.%20The%20vulnerability%20and%20fault%20lie%20in%20using%20networked%20machines%2C%20in%20which%20citizens%20had%20little%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20benign%20beauty%20of%20India's%20EVMs%20is%20that%20they%20are%20designed%20for%20a%2021st-century%20electronic%20gadget%2C%20and%20hence%20this%20makes%20them%20tamper-proof%20and%20hacking-resistant%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20an%20expert%20from%20IIT-Bombay%20who%20assisted%20the%20ECI%20in%20designing%20the%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%205.5%20million%20EVMs%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20and%20each%20is%20a%20standalone%20device%20almost%20akin%20to%20a%20basic%20calculator.%20Even%20the%20latest%20third-generation%20EVMs%2C%20the%20M3%20machines%20that%20the%20ECI%20is%20using%2C%20are%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20internet%20and%20cannot%20connect%20to%20Bluetooth.%20This%20makes%20them%20impenetrable%20through%20remote%20devices%2C%20and%20the%20M3%20machines%2C%20if%20they%20are%20opened%20or%20tampered%20with%2C%20are%20designed%20to%20go%20into%20a%20safety%20mode%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20inoperable%20and%20only%20the%20original%20manufacturer%20can%20reset%20the%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20foreign%20experts%20have%20often%20complained%20that%20India's%20EVMs%20are%20antiquated%20and%20need%20to%20be%20modernized.%20However%2C%20experts%20at%20ECI%20say%20sometimes%20being%20obsolete%20gives%20electronic%20technology%20that%20level%20of%20extra%20security%2C%20since%20if%20one%20has%20to%20hack%20EVMs%2C%20then%205.5%20million%20individual%20EVMs%20will%20have%20to%20be%20hacked%2C%20which%20is%20a%20near%20impossibility%2C%20and%20subsequently%2C%20the%20randomization%20provides%20that%20additional%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20Indian%20EVMs%20and%20digital%20voting%20are%20considered%20the%20gold%20standard.%20India's%20pioneering%20innovation%20of%20EVMs%20empowers%201.4%20billion%20Indians%20to%20vote%20freely%20and%20fairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715947080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Ffpcf6j4s_evm-generic_625x300_10_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-india-1st-country-in-the-world-to-use-evms-5684833%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%2C%20but%20not%20many%20know%20that%20it%20is%20India%20which%20perfected%20and%20deployed%20mass%20electronic%20voting%20for%20the%20first%20time%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-india-1st-country-in-the-world-to-use-evms-5684833%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-india-1st-country-in-the-world-to-use-evms-5684833%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-india-1st-country-in-the-world-to-use-evms-5684833%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Janhvi%3A%20Shikhar%20has%20been%20a%20constant%20support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715946981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110210400%2Cimgsize-38904.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.in