5C%22%3EYour%20privacy%20is%20protected%20because%20all%20the%20data%20used%20for%20Eye%20Tracking%20stays%20on%20your%20device.%20It%20is%20not%20even%20shared%20with%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEye%20Tracking%20works%20with%20all%20apps%20on%20iPadOS%20and%20iOS%20so%20no%20extra%20hardware%20or%20accessories%20are%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsing%20Eye%20Tracking%2C%20users%20can%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENavigate%20through%20different%20parts%20of%20an%20app%20by%20looking%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUse%20Dwell%20Control%20to%20activate%20these%20elements.%20This%20means%20that%20they%20can%20select%20a%20part%20of%20the%20screen%20by%20focusing%20their%20gaze%20on%20that%20part%20of%20the%20screen%20for%20a%20short%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEye%20Tracking%20allows%20users%20to%20perform%20actions%20such%20as%20pressing%20buttons%2C%20swiping%2C%20and%20other%20gestures%20using%20only%20their%20eyes%2C%20without%20needing%20physical%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EApple%20CEO%2C%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fin%2Fnewsroom%2F2024%2F05%2Fapple-announces-new-accessibility-features-including-eye-tracking%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20believed%20that%20innovation%20enriches%20lives%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthat's%20why%20for%20nearly%2040%20years%2C%20Apple%20has%20championed%20inclusive%20design%20by%20embedding%20accessibility%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20hardware%20and%20software.%E2%80%9D%20He%20stated%20that%20Apple%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuously%20pushing%20the%20boundaries%20of%20technolo