ar%2C%20barged%20into%20the%20room.%20Swati%20Maliwal%20said%20he%20started%20screaming%20at%20her%20without%20provocation%20and%20abusing%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20she%20was%20stunned%20by%20the%20sudden%20attack%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20stop.%20She%20also%20urged%20him%20to%20call%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20allegedly%20kept%20shouting%20at%20her%2C%20and%20demanded%20to%20know%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20authority%20she%20had%20to%20question%20him%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20alleges%20that%20he%20started%20slapping%20her%20and%20%26quot%3Bslapped%20her%207-8%20times%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20she%20kept%20screaming.%20Ms%20Maliwal%20says%20she%20felt%20numb%20and%20shocked%20and%20screamed%20for%20help%20over%20and%20over%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20protect%20herself%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20allegedly%20pushed%20Kumar%20away%20with%20her%20legs.%20She%20alleges%20that%20he%20pounced%20on%20her%2C%20dragged%20her%2C%20and%20deliberately%20pulled%20her%20shirt%20up.%20The%20buttons%20broke.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20claims%20she%20hit%20her%20head%20on%20the%20center%20table%20before%20landing%20on%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwati%20Maliwal%20said%20she%20was%20constantly%20screaming%20for%20help%20but%20no%20one%20came.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBibhav%20Kumar%2C%20she%20says%2C%20did%20not%20relent%20and%20kicked%20her%20chest%2C%20stomach%2C%20and%20pelvis%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20she%20was%20in%20extreme%20pain%20and%20kept%20asking%20him%20to%20stop.%20Her%20shirt%20was%20coming%20up%20but%20he%20continued%20to%20assault%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Maliwal%20repeatedly%20told%20him%20that%20she%20was%20on%20her%20period%20and%20that%20he%20should%20let%20her%20go%20as%20she%20was%20in%20unbearable%20pain.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20says%20she%20somehow%20managed%20to%20free%20herself%2C%20sat%20on%20the%20sofa%20and%20picked%20up%20her%20spectacles%20from%20the%20floor.%3C%