0and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20moved%20from%20a%20private%20label%20to%20manufacturing%20100%20percent%20of%20their%20own%20products%20in%202018%20from%20their%20sprawling%20factory%20in%20Pune%2C%20where%20over%20seven%20lakh%20of%20their%20products%20are%20manufactured%20each%20month.%20Their%20bestsellers%20are%20oats%2C%20chia%20seeds%20and%20muesli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Holding%20on%20to%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2013-year%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth.%20The%20duo%20pumped%20in%20more%20than%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20in%20the%20initial%20few%20years%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20draw%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years.%20For%20the%20next%20three%2C%20they%20drew%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22True%20Elements%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20products%20%E2%80%94from%20breakfast%2C%20snacks%20and%20dry%20fruits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785-500x250.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785-768x384.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSequence-01.00_00_26_44.Still001-1715862785-150x75.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350278%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%2