alaries.%20But%20COVID-19%20was%20a%20tough%20time%20as%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20money.%20We%20asked%20our%20employees%20personally%20as%20to%20who%20would%20be%20okay%20with%20a%20deferment%20of%20salary%2C%20and%20we%20were%20just%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20response.%20Their%20wholehearted%20willingness%20and%20trust%20in%20us%20pulled%20us%20through%20and%20we%20paid%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20salaries%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20share%20that%20during%20every%20crisis%2C%20it%20is%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20that%20has%20kept%20them%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20a%20brand%20that%20will%20outlive%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20creating%20their%20own%20brand%20was%20so%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20value%20to%20people%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20outliving%20the%20founders.%20This%20led%20to%20Marico%20acquiring%20about%2054%25%20equity%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22True%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-300x291.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-500x484.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-768x744.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Ftrue1-1715860659-150x145.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350256%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrue%20Elements%20has%20a%20factory%20in%20Pune%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20choose%20a%20partner%20who%20would%20align%20with%20our%20vision%20and%20understand%20health.%20We%20both%20were%20also%20clear%2C%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20would%20outlive%20us.%20This%20acquisition%20would%20help%20our%20objective%20come%20true%20and%20make%20%E2%80%98True%20Elements%E2%80%99%20a%20household%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20COO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20healthy%20food%20space%2C%20the%20founders%20believe%20that%20their%20differentiation%20lies%20in%20the%20transparency%20with%20regard%20to%20their%20products.%20All%20their%20products%20have%20complete%20ingredients%20listed%20behind%20them%20and%20an%20option%20to%20trace%20the%20ingredient%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20farm%20to%20fork%20on%20their%20website%20using%20the%20product%20name%20and%20batch%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20share%20that%20their%20startup%20rests%20on%20four%20pillars%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CTrue%20to%20our%20food%20(nutrition)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20word%20(transparency)%2C%20true%20to%20our%20planet%20(recycle)%2C%20and%20true%20to%20our%20families%20(people).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20completely%20honest%20about%20what%20we%20put%20in%20our%20products%20by%20naming%20it%20all%20on%20the%20pack.%20We%20ensure%20that%20we%20even%20mention%20ingredients%20that%20aren%E2%80%99t%20compulsory%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20stand%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20a%20plastic-neutral%20brand%2C%20wherein%20all%20the%20plastic%20that%20they%20are%20using%20is%20recycled.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20process%20about%2030%20percent%20directly%2C%20while%20we%20have%20a%20partner%20who%20processes%20the%20remaining.%20It%20is%20converted%20into%20biofuel%20and%20supplied%20to%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20Elements%20is%20a%20certified%20%E2%80%98Clean%20Label%E2%80%99%20brand%20by%20the%20Clean%20Label%20Project%2C%20US%2C%20and%20100%20percent%20whole%20grain%20brand%20by%20the%20Whole%20Grains%20Council%2C%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20presence%20built%20around%20300%20towns%20in%20India%20with%20over%20300%20employees%2C%20supplying%20to%20over%20five%20lakh%20households%20every%20month%2C%20the%20duo%20are%20working%20towards%20their%20mission%20of%20providing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indians.%20They%20are%20clear%20on%20their%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20clean%20food%20%E2%80%94%20the%20reason%20they%20stay%20away%20from%20products%20like%20protein%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20their%20message%20to%20budding%20entrepreneurs%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20overthink%2C%20just%20start%20up.%20There%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfect%20time.%20Dive%20in%20with%20a%20childlike%20mindset%2C%20and%20just%20like%20children%20do%20when%20they%20fall%20down%2C%20stand%20up%20and%20try%20again.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fall%20down%20and%20fail.%20Shun%20the%20need%20for%20validation%20and%20fear%20of%20judgement%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Puru.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20youngsters%20who%20believe%20that%20you%20can%20succeed%20in%20a%20year%2C%20Sreejith%20has%20some%20words%20of%20wisdom.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20arrives%20in%20a%20year%2C%20it%20takes%20at%20least%20six%20years.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20up%20before%20these%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20be%20afraid%20of%20going%20down%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sreejith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20True%20Elements%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715929549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FCover-image-15-1715860333.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sreejith%20Moolayil%20and%20Puru%20Gupta%20overcame%20challenges%20to%20build%20their%20healthy%20food%20brand%2C%20True%20Elements.%20Despite%20early%20failures%20and%20financial%20struggles%2C%20their%20commitment%20to%20preventative%20healthcare%20and%20transparency%20led%20to%20a%20multi-crore%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350165%2Fpuru-gupta-sreejith-moolayil-true-elements-pune-marico-healthy-snacks-rolled-oats-muesli-chia-seeds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20plans%20to%20float%20nuclear%20reactors%20in%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20analysts%20see%20it%20'risky%20for%20environment'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715929211000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110199667%2Cimgsize-632553.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-plans-to-float-nuclear-reactors-in-disputed-south-china-sea-analysts-see-it-risky-for-environment%2Farticleshow%2F110199630.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110199630.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20military%20warned%20that%20China%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20developing%20floating%20nuclear%20reactors%20in%