t%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349615%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20his%20parents%2C%20Subrat%20believes%20in%20giving%20traditional%20fertilisers%20to%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20fruiting%20plant%20requires%20nitrogen%20for%20leaves%20and%20stem%20growth%2C%20phosphorus%20for%20root%20development%2C%20and%20potash%20for%20flower%20and%20fruit%20growth.%20We%20get%20these%20nutrients%20in%20cow%20dung%20itself.%20I%20do%20not%20make%20any%20other%20fancy%20fertilisers.%20Cow%20dung%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Subrat%20does%20not%20aim%20to%20sell%20the%20Miyazaki%20mangoes%2C%20he%20does%20sell%20saplings%20of%20the%20rare%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20and%20other%20water%20lily%20varieties.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20grow%20any%20rare%20plant%2C%20one%20must%20do%20a%20detailed%20study%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20they%20require%20and%20the%20pot%20size.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20grow%20the%201%2C