aping%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20food%20we%E2%80%99re%20putting%20into%20our%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20has%20become%20integral%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20whether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20Therefore%2C%20making%20conscious%20decisions%20to%20opt%20for%20packaged%20foods%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20pose%20additional%20risks%20is%20essential.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20our%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20have%20emphasised%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20carefully%20reading%20food%20labels.%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20released%20dietary%20guidelines%20for%20Indians%20on%20May%208%2C%20cautioning%20that%20the%20information%20provided%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaged%20food%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20often%20be%20misleading.%20%E2%80%9CHealth%20claims%20on%20packaged%20food%20are%20designed%20to%20catch%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20attention%20and%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20product%20is%20healthy.%20Always%20read%20food%20label%20information%20to%20know%20about%20the%20contents%20inside%20the%20pack%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20guidelines%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20fooled%20by%20labels%20like%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98no%20sugar%20added%E2%80%99.%20One%20man%20who%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20decode%20these%20food%20labels%20and%20teach%20Indians%20how%20to%20read%20them%20is%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20aka%20%E2%80%98foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20this%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20promoting%20health%20literacy%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20making%20purchases.%20Through%20his%20Instagram%20page%2C%20he%20has%20gathered%20a%20following%20of%20over%202.2%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20left%20behind%20a%20lucrative%20Rs%202%20crore%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20this%20certified%20health%20coach%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spark%20a%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20health%20literate.%20I%E2%80%99m%20therefore%20focusing%20on%20health%20literacy%2C%20with%20my%20major%20target%20being%20children.%20You%20should%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20in%20children%20from%20day%20one%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20junk%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20health%20issues%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20large%20FMCG%20conglomerates%20accountable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%2090s%20Kolkata%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20regular%20childhood%2C%20which%20included%20biscuits%2C%20packaged%20foods%2C%20and%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita.%20The%20young%20boy%20was%20then%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20the%20food%20he%20consumed%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Revant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350079%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERevant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20slowly%20learnt%20the%20importance%20of%20nutrition%20over%20the%20second%20decade%20of%20his%20life%2C%20which%20he%20spent%20largely%20in%20the%20US.%20Revant%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20for%20his%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20finance%20and%20management%20in%202011.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20time%20that%20he%20started%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20food%20and%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20eventually%20got%20cemented%20with%20a%20health%20coach%20certification%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20started%20reading%20food%20labels%20carefully%20during%20his%20grocery%20store%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20eat%20healthy%20and%20started%20paying%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20ingredient%20list.%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20most%20companies%20are%20saying%20something%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20while%20the%20back%20states%20a%20different%20story.%20I%20slowly%20learnt%20about%20the%20ingredients%20like%20the%20emulsifiers%2C%20colours%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20angered%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20while%20the%20company%20states%20that%20the%20product%20is%20natural%2C%20organic%2C%20and%20very%20good%20for%20you%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20far%20from%20it.%20This%20led%20to%20intense%20research%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20nutrition%20and%20food%20labels%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20creating%20social%20impact%20and%20looked%20at%20various%20avenues%20where%20I%20could%20provide%20help.%20I%20realised%20that%20health%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20pillars%20of%20life%2C%20and%20what%20we%20eat%20directly%20impacts%20it.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20solving%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20structured%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Revant%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490-500x608.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Revant%20quit%20a%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20nutrition%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490-500x608.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490-247x300.jpeg%20247w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490-768x934.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490-150x182.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-15-at-16.04.14-min-1-1715769490.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350045%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERevant%20quit%20a%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%20to%20educate%20people%20about%20nutrition.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20his%20desire%20to%20create%20impact%20first%20materialised%20as%20a%20self-book%20called%20Selfienomics%20in%202016%2C%20which%20interestingly%20had%20information%20on%20reading%20food%20labels!%20While%20he%20had%20realised%20the%20importance%20of%20this%20topic%2C%20it%20was%20seven%20years%20later%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20the%20mission%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20his%20%E2%80%98Bournvita%E2%80%99%20video%20that%20led%20to%20him%20becoming%20a%20bonafide%20viral%20sensation%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20April%202023%2C%20Revant%20worked%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%20at%20McKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%20His%20stint%20at%20the%20management%20consulting%20firm%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20his%20content%20today.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20consultant%2C%20I%20often%20worked%20on%20projects%20in%20the%20grocery%20space%2C%20so%20I%20know%20first-hand%20about%20the%20false%20marketing%20that%20takes%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20consulting%20meant%20solving%20problems%20in%20a%20structured%20manner.%20Revant%20decided%20to%20use%20this%20skill%20to%20help%20solve%20the%20larger%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20reading%20and%20understanding%20food%20labels.%20With%20this%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20clear%20about%20his%20mission%20and%20took%20on%20the%20baton%20of%20teaching%20Indians%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20important%20life%20skill%E2%80%9D.%20His%20problem%20lies%20with%20packaged%20food%20that%20masquerades%20as%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20he%20kicked%20off%20his%20stint%20as%20%E2%80%98Foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20video%20about%20Bournvita%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Mondelez.%20The%20video%20highlighted%20the%20excessive%20amount%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20drink%2C%20yet%20calling%20itself%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20diabetes.%20The%20video%20went%20viral%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20trouble%20for%20the%20former%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20sent%20him%20a%20legal%20notice%20asking%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video.%20Left%20with%20no%20choice%2C%20Revant%20took%20it%20down%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20achieved%20what%20he%20set%20out%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20create%20awareness%20among%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStay%20away%20from%20sugary%20drinks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20legal%20notice%2C%20Cadbury%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20by%2014.4%20percent%20in%20December%202023%2C%20validating%20the%20content%20creator%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20The%20Central%20Government%20also%20directed%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20Bournvita%20and%20other%20such%20drinks%20from%20the%20health%20drinks%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20product%20that%20reduced%20its%20sugar%20content%20by%2022%20percent%20was%20%E2%80%98Maggi%20rich%20tomato%20ketchup%E2%80%99.%20Revant%20made%20a%20video%20highlighting%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20product%20had%20more%20sugar%20than%20tomatoes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20actions%20have%20been%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20content%20creator%2C%20who%20has%20since%20educated%20Indians%20on%20many%20other%20packaged%20products.%20His%20problem%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20with%20the%20false%20marketing%20by%20companies%2C%20which%20promise%20nutrition%2C%20strength%20and%20more%20for%20your%20child%2C%20when%20actually%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20filled%20with%20sugar.%20His%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20chocolates%20or%20Coke%20as%20much%20as%20with%20dri