is%20a%20tough%20terrain%20for%20us%20to%20access.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20adds%20that%20they%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20plant%20species%20after%20thorough%20research%20through%20Vedic%20literature%20as%20well%20as%20the%20IUCN%20lists.%20Once%20they%20demarcate%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20plants%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20care%20not%20to%20publicise%20it%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20they%20take%20the%20GPS%20coordinates%20of%20the%20place%20and%20in%20the%20months%20that%20follow%2C%20conduct%20studies%20on%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20plant%20species%20conserved%20is%20the%20Himalayan%20Gentian%20(%3Cem%3EGentiana%20Kurroo)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20striking%20blue-coloured%20flower%2C%20that%20has%20highly%20medicinal%20roots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20it%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20excessive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171244%2Fkarnataka-farmer-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover-exploitation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaturvedi%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20treat%20liver%20problems%20makes%20it%20a%20target%20of%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Research%20Wing%20of%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Forest%20Department%2C%20approximately%20600%20Himalayan%20Gentian%20specimens%20have%20been%20successfully%20conserved%20across%20three%20different%20regions%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1-1715249843.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Himalayan%20Gentian's%20roots%20are%20said%20to%20have%20medicinal%20properties%5C%22%20srcset%3D