ave%20huge%20respect%20for%20her.%20She%20has%20designed%20each%20and%20everything%20in%20such%20a%20connected%20manner%3B%20every%20moss%2C%20every%20lichen%2C%20every%20insect%2C%20every%20pollinator.%20They%20are%20all%20so%20beautifully%20interconnected%20with%20each%20other%20that%20if%20you%20take%20out%20even%20one%20string%2C%20the%20entire%20chain%20will%20be%20disturbed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20save%20and%20foster%20Uttarakhand's%20miracle%20plants%20like%20Patwa%2C%20Himalayan%20Lily%20and%20Gentiana%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349417%2Fifs-officer-sanjeev-chaturvedi-uttarakhand-endangered-plants-conservation-patwa-gentiana-lilium-polyphyllum%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98How%20I%20Got%20a%20Job%20At%20NASA%E2%80%99%3A%20Aerospace%20Engineer%20Shares%205%20Tips%20to%20Build%20a%20Career%20in%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAkshata%20Krishnamurthy%E2%80%99s%20fascination%20with%20space%20began%20as%20a%20child%20as%20she%20wondered%20about%20what%20lies%20beyond%20our%20planet.%20Her%20curiosity%20was%20fuelled%20by%20weekly%20visits%20to%20the%20planetariums%20and%20air%20shows%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20would%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20aerospace.%20But%20how%2C%20where%2C%20and%20what%20to%20do%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream%20was%20a%20path%20she%20had%20to%20navigate%20on%20her%