%20robotics%20project%20as%20these%20are%20going%20to%20be%20used%20in%20space%20technologies%20being%20developed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplete%20research%20projects%20in%20well-known%20institutes%20and%20develop%20expertise%20in%20an%20area%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetwork%2C%20Network%2C%20Network.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETry%20to%20build%20a%20professional%20network%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20by%20attending%20conferences%2C%20workshops%2C%20professional%20seminars%20and%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20any%20talks%20in%20planetariums%20or%20research%20institutes%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20attend%20them.%20You%20can%20ask%20questions%20to%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20what%20you%20want%20to.%20You%20could%20find%20a%20mentor%20or%20it%20will%20at%20least%20help%20you%20chart%20your%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Akshata%20Krishnamurthy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F1715219850.743726-min-1715319952.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshata%20Krishnamurthy%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20getting%20a%20job%20at%20NASA%20as%20an%20aerospace%20engineer%20is%20a%20nail-biter.%20From%20humble%20beginnings%20in%20Bengaluru%20to%20a%20fully-funded%20scholarship%20at%20MIT%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20built%20a%20career%20in%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349546%2Fakshata-krishnamurthy-nasa-aerospace-engineer-rocket-scientist-space-career-mit%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20Takes%20A%20Virtual%20Village%3A%2010%20Online%20Groups%20Helping%20New%20Moms%20Navigate%20Parenting%20Challenges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20baby%20wakes%20up%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20lay%20her%20on%20the%20bed.%20What%20should%20I%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20you%20make%20your%20baby%20comfortable%20with%20other%20caretakers%3F%20I%20need%20to%20start%20work%20next%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20hair%20fall.%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20will%20go%20bald%20soon.%20What%20can%20I%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20starting%20solids%20soon.%20What%20should%20I%20start%20with%3F%20Should%20I%20follow%20baby-led%20weaning%20or%20traditional%20weaning%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20a%20village%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20a%20child%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ask%20any%20mother%2C%20and%20she%20will%20agree.%20Earlier%2C%20these%20villages%20were%20found%20quite%20literally%2C%20in%20homes%2C%20and%20neighbourhoods.%20When%20we%20were%20growing%20up%2C%20we%20would%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20playing%20downstairs%20or%20in%20our%20neighbours%E2%80%99%20houses.%20In%20joint%20family%20settings%2C%20the%20village%20was%20present%20within%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20increasingly%20nuclear%20households%2C%20we%2C%20as%20mothers%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20that%20privilege.%20This%20leads%20us%20to%20look%20for%20villages%20in%20the%20virtual%20world.%20Since%20we%20also%20want%20to%20raise%20our%20children%20using%20modern%20methods%20and%2C%20often%20being%20single%20children%20or%20having%20just%20one%20sibling%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20seek%20support%20from%20peers%20experiencing%20similar%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20navigating%20the