%20lot%20of%20different%20insects%20and%20birds%20flocking%20in%20the%20area%20such%20as%20Rent%20Vented%20Bulbul%2C%20Common%20Tailorbird%2C%20Gray%20Treepie%20etc%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ahana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%2048%20hours%20at%20Palighar%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20spending%20your%20time%20admiring%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20cottages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20activities%20that%20you%20can%20indulge%20in%20at%20the%20Palighar%20Homestay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%2C%20the%20brains%20behind%20the%20activities%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20destination%2C%20Palighar%20is%20outside%20the%20town%20area%20of%20Kalimpong.%20The%20guests%20who%20ideally%20come%20and%20stay%20with%20us%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20calm%20vacation%20and%20that%20is%20what%20we%20try%20to%20give%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20guests%20arrive%2C%20the%20couple%20briefs%20them%20about%20the%20property%20and%20the%20surroundings.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20they%20have%20settled%20in%2C%20we%20also%20give%20them%20a%20list%20of%20activities%20that%20we%20do.%20The%20guests%20can%20walk%20with%20us%20and%20trek%20to%20the%20villages%20nearby%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kabir%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20trek%2C%20we%20encourage%20them%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20villagers%20and%20understand%20their%20ways%20of%20living.%20If%20our%20guests%20are%20interested%2C%20we%20also%20explain%20the%20various%20aspects%20of%20terrace%20farming%20with%20a%20live%20demonstration.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20guests%20can%20also%20go%20on%20a%20longer%20trek%20to%2